OL,5, The son of a bus driver murdered by the
OL,6, IRA on Bloody Friday in Belfast has    
OL,7, said he would like to know the full    
OL,8, truth of what happened.                
OL,10,FNine people died and more than 130 were
OL,11,Finjured when 19 bombs exploded in      
OL,12,Flittle over an hour on 21 July 1972.   
OL,14,FRobert Gibson, whose father Jackie, 45,
OL,15,Fwas killed at Oxford Street bus        
OL,16,Fstation, said: "The truth is something 
OL,17,Feverybody deserves."                   
OL,19,FHe believes there may be people still  
OL,20,Falive who can provide answers.         
